				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">We don't "need" cold based spells, either.  It's been beat to death that wizards and druids will have the three flavours of nukes and mages will make do with 2, with pets filling the missing "cold" flavour when needed.  I originally felt we should have the variety while wizards had the specialty, but even after months in the elementals (and raiding in Fire, specifically) I think we can make do with magic and fire.
<br />

<br />
I think we could use an aggro-reducer or shifter, and definitely need an upgrade in pet DPS.  We also need our existing AAs looked at and tuned properly, or even changed in some cases.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=96985" target="_blank" class="postlink">Fazzadien Elementweaver</a> 
<br />
Arch Convoker
<br />
Prodigy of War - Kane Bayle
