				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It should be through pets.  Agreed, most people do.
<br />

<br />
The reality is, balancing through pets is Haaard (dev whine)
<br />

<br />
It is just too easy for pets strong enough to be used, to become unbalancing.
<br />

<br />
Increasing nuke efficiencies is EASY, and very easy to predict the effects on.  
<br />

<br />
Realistically our pet plus us should be top damage in MOST situations, why, because frankly, it is about all we have, and the thought of giving our pets what they need to balance us seems to give the devs screaming terrors.
<br />

<br />
If they can't bring themselves to fix us with our pets, then they had best upgrade us with our nukes.  Speed our casting and improve our efficiencies.  Wizards can be the lords of the big boom cannons, mages can be the chain guns.  Everybody gets their niche, nobody gets left behind.<br />_________________<br />Rondo</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
